The paper proposes a method for scene text localization, recognition, and script identification using convolutional neural nets. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of annotations and the challenges in obtaining accurate multi-language multi-script annotations, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories.
